Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.85,0:14:44.86,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.86,0:14:44.91,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.33,0:22:27.37,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
