Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.82,0:00:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who are bound by a contract may enter here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have awakened to your power most brilliantly.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the Contractor's Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.22,0:00:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From this night forth, you are our guest in the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.82,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Persona ability is that of the wild card.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that of others, it is very special.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.13,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It is like the number zero: Empty, yet holding infinite potential within itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.80,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to traveling the road of your destiny together
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to see where your awakened power of the wild card will take you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.79,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Satonaka! Wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd the monsters go?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone for good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who killed them!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was seriously amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you call it... "Persona," was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.99,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just get out of here before more of those things come.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.97,0:03:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An exit?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally found you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you know this place.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.18,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,First, tell me what happened to the Shadows!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean those monsters back there?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you provoke them?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear-ish the thought!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.69,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it up to here with people barging in here and riling up the Shadows!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,TVs?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now off with you! Beat it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a busy bear!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that bear.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.59,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.43,0:04:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!{I'm glad to be alive!}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take advantage of the situation!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same poster I saw over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's Hiiragi Misuzu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been on the news a lot lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.35,0:04:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband's the one who had the affair with the announcer that died.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.62,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. What about that freaky room?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be connected to the death of Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go there!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think my heart can take it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.41,0:04:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit, I forgot! I gotta go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is giving me the chills.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel so good. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through hell yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.30,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you some other time, but you probably won't believe me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're Yukiko, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for a while now, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out and have some fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You're scaring her!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Amagi challenge ain't that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, are you coming or not?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.93,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn bitch.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he want?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He was obviously asking you out on a date!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't tell?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cruel, Amagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the same thing to me last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go out then?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart already belongs to someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.02,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, she hasn't texted me back since yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen again?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Amagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.48,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She left after her family called her.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They needed her help at the inn.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What inn?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.00,0:07:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her family owns the nicest traditional inn in town.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yukiko is the heir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?{senpai=Konishi}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She still hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The principal has something to say, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.69,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking out of turn will earn you a spot on my shit list!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So pipe down!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.67,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret to inform you that I have a terrible announcement to make.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.12,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi Saki of Class 3-B was found dead early this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remain calm.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.26,0:07:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been assured by the faculty that she wasn't the victim of bullying.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.54,0:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body was hung like Ms. Yamano's.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a telephone pole this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.92,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.50,0:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you guys watch the Midnight Channel last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna talk about that now?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hear me out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.92,0:08:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was bothering me, so I watched it last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I saw Konishi on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.15,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our classmates saw Ms. Yamano on the Midnight Channel and claimed she was his soul mate.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.73,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I heard that Konishi vanished before her death, just like Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be a coincidence.{Could that :really: be a coincidence?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think people who show up on TV die?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.30,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how we saw a poster of Hiiragi Misuzu over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.41,0:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the TV world is connected to the murders?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.54,0:09:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi and Ms. Yamano may have gone in there at some point!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to come back once, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.87,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go in from the same location, maybe we'll meet that bear again.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maybe" isn't good enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I could really use your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka, I'm leaving you in charge of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.87,0:09:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, I tell you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This was never gonna work!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you two again!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same place after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are bear-y suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.87,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I can tell someone's been throwing people in here before the fog lifts.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.11,0:10:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that if it's foggy on your side, the fog lifts here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.81,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I do recall it being foggy on the days Ms. Yamano and Konishi died.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone forced you in here,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so you must be the one's throwing people in!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.82,0:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are the culprits!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.88,0:10:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that Konishi and Ms. Yamano were thrown into this world?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.37,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you guys did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just admit it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.63,0:11:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How do we know {\i1}you{\i0} didn't do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.51,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off that stupid costume and show us your face!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.10,0:11:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.73,0:11:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty! What's up with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you bear-y much.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, does {\i1}anything{\i0} faze you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.09,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll believe that you guys aren't the culprits.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to find the real guy who did all this.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop him!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.05,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to live here in peace.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this thing for real?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only ones who can do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you promise?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're going along with it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being way too nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You better help us out then, stupid bear.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can see so clearly with these on!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.37,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this looks like the shopping district.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I last saw a girl over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you dumb bear.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the girl you're talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She disappeared into that store.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her family's place.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish Junes would go under.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I heard that Konishi's daughter is working there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.82,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could she, with her family's business suffering like it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a troublesome child.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.68,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that talking?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.62,0:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saki, how many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.00,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the eldest daughter of the {Konishi }family who owns this liquor store, aren't you ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How dare you get a part-time job at Junes?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her dad's voice?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can we hear this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is someone there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the ticket I gave her.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never had the chance to say it...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.68,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always wanted to tell Hana...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that he was a real pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.21,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was only nice to him because he was the store manager's son.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.66,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he takes it completely the wrong way and gets all enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.91,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain in the ass?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who cares about Junes, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The liquor store, the shopping district, my parents...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish everything would just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.06,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying! This can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she's like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.09,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who thinks everything's a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, "me"?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Oh, my.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two Yosukes?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And coming here for Konishi's sake?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a load of shit.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.91,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You just came because you thought it sounded like a good time!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What else is there to do out in this shithole?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.64,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If all went well, hey, maybe you could even be a hero.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And your sweetheart's death was the perfect excuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Shadow...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The true self...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}your{\i0} Shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck that! I don't know you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.49,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Say it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. I'm me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not you anymore, see?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That Shadow's getting bigger!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.12,0:16:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Hanamura?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You really hit it hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.13,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing like me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.81,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing came from you, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.85,0:16:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You put on a good show of being carefree and happy-go-lucky...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause you're so terrified of being alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not me! I don't know you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's attracting nearby Shadows!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.96,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, if we don't stop him soon, this'll get grizzly!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how pathetic you really are!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's ask Hanamura to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The prince of Junes?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.77,0:17:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He thinks everyone depends on him because he's the manager's son.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a loser!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew you were a nuisance,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.81,0:17:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but you played the part of the good guy well!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Booyah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He takes it completely the wrong way and gets all enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.08,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked her out 'cause you're sick of living in the boonies!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to do something fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now disappear!{shadow yosuke}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Wrong guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You loved her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.86,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi, that is.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.73,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.23,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly loved her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She dumped ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wasn't lying,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was so ashamed that I didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To get along with others,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to change the way I acted.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.18,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I think I'm annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.93,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But my feelings for her were real.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's a part of me, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get down to it, all of this is me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Shut up, you brat!{if I hear one more uzzee I'm going to kill someone}{lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Now's your chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.74,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi!{TS sign: Burning up!}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is my...{yos}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...Persona.{yu}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.79,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You really saved my ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dude.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys came back!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.66,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The rope got cut off, and I had no idea what to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerve of you guys! You're such morons!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this! You guys suck!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Satonaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.89,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me ten steaks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me ten steaks.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.90,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we accept your terms for forgiveness, right, Narukami?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, it'll be beef bowls.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.87,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.46,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi and Ms. Yamano were thrown into that dangerous place.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.83,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The people who came in here were attacked by their Shadows,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(3133,3675,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}just like Yosuke was a while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone really did throw them in,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.88,0:21:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find the culprit and stop him!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} did, anyway.{You did, yeah.}{He says it in a way like "Yeah we ended up making a promise (thanks to you you nigger lol)"}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that, with you, I can find the culprit
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and solve the case.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it true that you're the manager, even though you're still in high school?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.26,0:23:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm only filling in for my mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.79,0:23:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're looking gorgeous in that kimono!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I don't know...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it true that Ms. Yamano stayed at your inn before she died?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.27,0:23:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's late again.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to do the dishes.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.92,0:24:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.83,0:24:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.47,0:24:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura! Narukami!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.66,0:24:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.67,0:24:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He bit me.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.51,0:24:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.81,0:24:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.97,0:24:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.01,0:24:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.92,0:24:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
